%h2 Editing COP question
- form_for @cop_question, builder: DefaultFormBuilder, url: admin_cop_question_path(@cop_question) do |form|
  = render :partial => form
  %ul{:class => "tools inline" :style => 'float: right;'}
    %li= link_to 'Cancel', admin_cop_questions_path, :class => 'cancel_large'
    %li= form.submit 'Save changes', :class => 'button'